248	&lt;/module&gt;
249	</code></pre></div>
250	        <p id="Example3-code">
251	          Such config doesn't allow next cases
252	          even code is aligned further to the right for better reading:
253	        </p>
254	        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-java">
